org.apache.hadoop.fs

Interface FSWrapper

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileContextTestWrapper, FileSystemTestWrapper, FSTestWrapper

    public interface FSWrapper
    Abstraction of filesystem operations that is essentially an interface extracted from FileContext.
